yingyinNormal.en: See, a long time ago, there was this family. The Papá, he was a musician.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很久很久以前，有这样的一个家庭，爸爸是一个音乐家。

yingyinNormal.en: But requesting 'I Ran' from a serious musician is just… it's too far.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是要求一个严肃的音乐家演奏逃跑这种歌... 太过分了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's not a fantasy. That man was Ernesto de la Cruz. The greatest musician of all time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是幻想，那个人是厄内斯托·德拉库斯，世界上最伟大的音乐家。

yingyinNormal.en: We do not speak of that musician. He is dead to this family. You're all dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别想了，我们不能再提那个音乐家了，他对我们家来说已经死了。你们都已经死了。

yingyinNormal.en: No manches. You played with Ernesto de la Cruz? The greatest musician of all time?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别逗我了，你以前跟厄内斯托·德拉库斯一起搞音乐吗？他可是有史以来最伟大的音乐家。

yingyinNormal.en: Mamá Coco's father was Ernesto de la Cruz. What are you talking about? I'm gonna be a musician.
yingyinNormal.zh: 曾祖母可可的爸爸，是厄内斯托·德拉库斯。你在胡说些什么？我要当音乐家。

yingyinNormal.en: My Lord! Did you just say "A serious musician"? I don't think so. Can I borrow what you're wearing? Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊！你刚刚是说一个“严肃的音乐家”吗？是啊。我能借你的外套吗？为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: What? The cornett, it's like a trumpet only smaller. I know what a cornett is. So you're a musician? Yep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？科尔内管，很像喇叭但是要小一些。我知道科尔内管是什么，所以你是音乐家咯？是。

yingyinNormal.en: Angry street musician. I would like to make you an arrangement. I will only play in that square when you are not playing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 愤怒的街头音乐家，我来帮你安排一下，你不在广场上演唱时我才表演。

yingyinNormal.en: And you, my great-great-grandson are meant to be a musician.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而你，我的曾曾孙，你也是为音乐而生的。

yingyinNormal.en: And the Mamá, she didn't have time to cry over that walk-away musician.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而这个妈妈，根本就没有时间为这个出走的负心汉而伤心。

yingyinNormal.en: This is why I don't like musicians. Bunch of self-important jerks. Hey, I'm a musician. You are?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我说我讨厌搞音乐的，一群自以为是的混蛋。嘿，我也搞音乐。好吧。你搞音乐吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, he's definitely not gay. Oh, ho ho, a definitely not gay musician sleeping on my girlfriend's couch. Yippee.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他肯定不是同性恋。肯定不是同性恋的音乐人睡在我女朋友的沙发上，真开心。
